snippet.textDisplay: Dear Coke Studio Pakistan, you should bring more locals and tribal people to showcase like her and give them more of a platform and voice. We don't want to see the typical, unoriginal, uninspiring, mainstream pop music all the time. We would rather see and support our Pakistani homegrown talent. Please ensure the artists, like the tribal women and men here, are paid and properly supported, but well done for giving them this platform! This is the sort of entertainment I am proud to share with my non-Pakistani people. This culture is something to be proud of.
